title: GTA Online
headline: GTA Online
subtitle: New Safeguard Deliveries
content:
In Safeguard deliveries, your job is to move high-value goods across the city without them falling into the wrong hands. You’ll be assigned a reinforced Brute Stockade and a delivery point, but expect trouble on the road. The more damage your vehicle takes, the less you’ll earn, and if it’s destroyed the job’s a bust.

Complete three Safeguard deliveries to complete the Weekly Challenge and get the Hands On Car Wash Overalls, plus earn a boosted bonus of GTA$200,000.
